Package: RSpice
Title: R Interface to the Ngspice Simulator
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Qianqian", "Shan", email = "qianqianshan.am@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), 
    person("Stephen D.", "Holland", email = "sdh4@iastate.edu", role = c("aut")),
    person("William Q.", "Meeker", email = "wqmeeker@iastate.edu", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Qianqian Shan <qianqianshan.am@gmail.com>	
Description: An implementation of the interface to allow users to run Ng-spice
     in R via the shared library of Ng-spice. It provides functions to control
     the simulator and read the feedback from Ngspice to R. By using this 
     package, it is possible to save and analyze the outputs from Ngspice
     in R.  
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.1)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
